problem_statement:
UI Elements - SelectMany useTranslation
### Describe the Bug.

The SelectMany field in Payload CMS currently does not support translations.

<img width="829" height="326" alt="Image" src="https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/045db6c1-a8c2-45a7-a707-fc359175875f" />

### Reproduction Steps

Currently, the SelectMany element does not support translations.
After checking the file node_modules/@payloadcms/ui/dist/elements/SelectMany/index.js, I noticed that useTranslation was previously included but is now commented out. It would be great if translation support could be properly implemented in a future release.

Is it possible to fix this in the next update?

